      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "屏幕上只有一个矩形窗口，我们只想看到窗口里面的画面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "可线段常常伸到窗口外面，超出的部分必须被剪掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "如何又快又准地剪掉窗外的部分？这就是线段裁剪问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-code",
      "line_id": "code-1",
      "filename": "concept-code-code-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-code-code-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22320,
      "text": "窗口的四条边把平面分成九个区域。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-code",
      "line_id": "code-2",
      "filename": "concept-code-code-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-code-code-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "给每个点一个四位编码，分别记录它在上、下、右、左哪个方向出界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-code",
      "line_id": "code-3",
      "filename": "concept-code-code-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-code-code-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.16,
      "size": 18576,
      "text": "窗口内的点，四位全是零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-trivial",
      "line_id": "triv-1",
      "filename": "concept-trivial-triv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-trivial-triv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "两端编码都是零，说明整段都在窗内，直接接受。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-trivial",
      "line_id": "triv-2",
      "filename": "concept-trivial-triv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-trivial-triv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.68,
      "size": 42912,
      "text": "两端编码按位与不为零，说明它们同在某条边外侧，整段可直接拒绝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-trivial",
      "line_id": "triv-3",
      "filename": "concept-trivial-triv-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-trivial-triv-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "这两步只用位运算，快到几乎不花时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-1",
      "filename": "concept-iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-iterate-iter-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "其余情况，就取一个在外的端点，求线段与那条边的交点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-2",
      "filename": "concept-iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-iterate-iter-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "用交点替换外面的端点，重新编码，再判断一次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "concept-iterate",
      "line_id": "iter-3",
      "filename": "concept-iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/concept-iterate-iter-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "如此反复，最多几步就收窄成窗口内的那一段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "点击画布移动测试线段的端点，看粉色的可见部分如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "把整条线段拖到窗外，它会被整体拒绝，一点都不显示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/line-clipping/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "区域码让我们用位运算快速接受或拒绝大多数线段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "line-clipping",
